      <title>阿达尼集团 (Adani Group) 790 亿美元的集会让 GQG 的拉吉夫·贾恩 (Rajiv Jain) 获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/adani-group-s-79-billion-rally-makes-a-winner-of-gqg-s-rajiv-jain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[事实证明，印度亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 上市股票的大幅反弹对新兴市场投资者拉吉夫·贾恩 (Rajiv Jain) 来说是一笔意外之财，而就在他的公司 GQG Partners Inc. 入股印度企业集团仅九个月后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/adani-group-s-79-billion-rally-makes-a-winner-of-gqg-s-rajiv-jain</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 10:47:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
