      <title>美国出口加剧供应过剩担忧，油价跌至五个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价连续第五个交易日下跌——触及7月初以来的最低点——美国大量出口以及对 OPEC+ 是否能够实现减产计划的疑虑引发了对供应过剩的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 00:01:50 GMT</pubDate>
